## unpackRsc() function

Unpack an RSC file into the [entries](./rsc-tools.rscentry.md) that compose it

**Signature:**

```typescript
export declare function unpackRsc(arrayBuffer: ArrayBufferLike, options?: UnpackOptions): RscEntry[];
```

[RscEntry](./rsc-tools.rscentry.md)<!-- -->\[\]

The [entries](./rsc-tools.rscentry.md) contained within the arrayBuffer parameter

## Remarks

This function creates views over the buffer passed as argument. Modifying the content of an [entry](./rsc-tools.rscentry.md) will modify the buffer passed in this function and vice versa.
